snippet.title: EVE: Valkyrie - Warzone B-Roll
snippet.description:
EVE: Valkyrie - Warzone welcomes non-VR players to the first ever cross-platform, cross-reality, first-person spaceship shooter. 

New weapons, Ultra abilities and a modular progression system give you more control over how you evolve your fleet of next-generation ships. New maps and a new game mode - Extraction - give you exciting new ways to play. 

Born in VR, reborn for everyone. Welcome to the Warzone. 

Learn More: http://www.evevalkyrie.com/warzone
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/evevalkyrie
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/evevalkyrie
